    <h1>Let's celebrate the lunar new year</h1>

    <p>
      Chinese New Year, known in modern Chinese as the "Spring Festival", is an important Chinese festival celebrated at the turn of the traditional lunisolar Chinese calendar. 
    </p>

    <p>
      To celebrate this event, TGS asked us to set up a landing page where users could enter a competition by participating in an online "Cups and balls" game. Users would enter their birthyear and if they pick the right cup a fortune cookie would open with a message based on their year and sign.
