    <h2>SVG animation to the rescue</h2>

    <p>
      Having previously done a lot of manipulating of svg's I've realized that for this animation we should stick with implementing simple animations on more 'complex' svg drawings. The benefit of using the whole drawing as an svg is that it is automatically responsive.
    </p>


