   <h2>How a simple game can get pretty complex</h2>

   <p>
     The complete animation is done with the GSAP library and consists out of multiple generated timelines and a random placement of the fortune cookie under one of the cups. Using GSAP's curve path animation the cups always move along the same curved lines left or right.
   </p>

   <p>
     The animation consists of 3 rounds, each round speeding up the movement of the shuffling motion.
   </p>

